    "body": "\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Improvements**\n  * Added two FP8 reduced-precision float formats with bfloat16→FP8 conversion support for CUDA paths.\n  * Unified type-mapping so GEMM kernels resolve runtime numeric types via the new mapping layer, reducing type-mismatch risk and improving precision handling.\n\n* **Chores**\n  * Minor import and code hygiene cleanup.\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
